data.description: H12129. Welcome to this light, bright and freshly painted home with a great location.  This 4 Bedroom, 2 Bath, 2 Car-Garage concrete block home that is located in a quiet and friendly neighborhood with NO HOA FEES and less than a 10-minute drive to the lovely Downtown Bonita Springs and just 8 miles to Bonita Beach! As you enter your eyes will be drawn to the voluminous ceilings and open feel of this home.This home features A NEW ROOF (2021) AND NEW AIR CONDITIONER (2023), ALL NEW Carpet 11/23 , New screen front entry door,  tile throughout the main living areas, vaulted ceilings, fans and light fixtures throughout. The kitchen has granite countertops, white shaker style cabinetry, and stainless-steel appliances.The primary bedroom is spacious with an en-suite bathroom with walk-in shower. Enjoy beginning and ending your day on your screened-in back lanai while taking in your tranquil green private backyard view! There is an extended lanai area to Grill out next to your lanai with a side walk to the driveway. This home has fabulous elevation.Bonita Springs High School and Charter School are close by and only a 10 minute drive to Coconut Point Mall and short drive to RSW airport
